[[SOFTWARE_FUNCTION]]
UID: SF-005
TITLE: Extension Framework
STATEMENT: >>>
Model-based extensibility for type Handler, renderers, and Data View.
<<<
DESCRIPTION: >>>
Groups requirements for the extension mechanism that enables custom models to provide type handlers, TERM-34, data view generators, and style presets.
<<<
RATIONALE: >>>
Extensibility through model directories enables domain-specific customization without modifying the core pipeline.
<<<
RELATIONS:
- TYPE: Parent
